{"id":1024217729,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"3 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1692296519,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"28 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1024217729/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"13.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        set<char> charSet;\n        int left=0,right=left,n=s.size(),maxSubLength=0;\n        while(right<n)\n        if(charSet.find(s[right])==charSet.end()){\n            charSet.insert(s[right]);\n            maxSubLength=max(maxSubLength,right-left+1);\n            right++;\n        }\n        else{\n            charSet.erase(s[left]);\n            left++;\n        }\n        return maxSubLength;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
